{"id":3573,"date":"2016-12-24T08:58:18","date_gmt":"2016-12-24T08:58:18","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/?p=3573"},"modified":"2017-02-16T21:23:58","modified_gmt":"2017-02-16T21:23:58","slug":"jafar-al-sadiq-descendant-abu-bakr","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/2016\/12\/24\/jafar-al-sadiq-descendant-abu-bakr\/","title":{"rendered":"Jafar Al-Sadiq is a Descendant of Abu Bakr"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/imgstore.org\/a\/67hxw0egsgub?i=3573\" alt=\"\" \/><\/p>\n<h1 class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Jafar Al-Sadiq is a Descendant of Abu Bakr<\/span><\/h1>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">In the name of Allah the Most Gracious and Most Merciful&#8230;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">The following article will provide conclusive proof that Jafar Al-Sadiq is a descendant of Abu Bakr, from Sunni and Shia sources. The article will also include a refutation to a desperate Shia attempt to weaken one of these narrations in which Jafar speaks highly of his great-grandfather.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">The article will be split into the following sections:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0Jafar Al-Sadiq is a descendent of Abu Bakr (Sunni Sources)<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0Jafar Al-Sadiq is a descendent of Abu Bakr (Shia Sources)<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0Jafar Al-Sadiq Proudly Claims that he is a Descendant of Abu Bakr<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0Shia Attempt to Respond to the Narration<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0Conclusion<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Jafar Al-Sadiq is a descendent of Abu Bakr (Sunni Sources)<\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Ibn Sa\u2019ad (230 AH) in his Tabaqat 7\/543 said:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Jafar bin Mohammad bin Ali bin Husain bin Abi bin Abi Talib. His mother\u2019s name is Um Farwa bint Al-Qasim bin Mohammad bin Abi Bakr Al-Siddeeq.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Ibn Hibban (354 AH) in his Thiqaat 3\/251 said:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">The mother of Jafar bin Mohammad is Um Farwa bint Al-Qassim bin Mohammad bin Abi Bakr Al-Siddeeq.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Jafar Al-Sadiq is a descendent of Abu Bakr (Shia Sources)<\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Al-Mufeed (413 AH) in Al-Irshad p. 262 said:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">His (Jafar\u2019s) mother is Um Farwa bint Mohammad bin Abi Bakr.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Al-Tusi (460AH) in his Tahtheeb Al-Ahkam 6\/1345 said:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">His (Jafar\u2019s) mother is Um Farwa bint Al-Qassim bin Mohammad the generous bin Abi Bakr.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Jafar Al-Sadiq Proudly Claims that he is a Descendant of Abu Bakr<\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">In an authentic narration in Musnad Musadad, Jafar praises Abu Bakr then states: \u201cHe gave birth to me twice.\u201d (See ItHaaf Al-Maharah #8852)<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tm6\"><a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/20161224_105937.png\" rel=\"external nofollow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-3574 alignleft\" src=\"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/20161224_105937-150x150.png\" alt=\"jafar al-sadiq\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/20161224_105937-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/20161224_105937-250x250.png 250w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/20161224_105937-62x62.png 62w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/20161224_105937-184x184.png 184w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/><\/a>This statement might seem strange, but those that are familiar with the geneology of Jafar Al-Sadiq will not be surprised. We have included an image of the <\/span><em><span class=\"tm7\">nasab<\/span><\/em><span class=\"tm6\"> of Jafar for the sake of clarity.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Ayatollah Qazwini\u2019s Attempt to Respond to the Narration<\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tm6\"><a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/IMG-20161222-WA0036.jpg\" rel=\"external nofollow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-3575 alignleft\" src=\"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/IMG-20161222-WA0036-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"img-20161222-wa0036\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/IMG-20161222-WA0036-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/IMG-20161222-WA0036-250x250.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/IMG-20161222-WA0036-62x62.jpg 62w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/IMG-20161222-WA0036-184x184.jpg 184w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/><\/a><\/span><span class=\"tm6\">Below, we find a response to the previous narration from the <\/span><u><a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/www.valiasr-aj.com\/english\/shownews.php?idnews=411\" rel=\"external nofollow\"><span class=\"tm8\">valiasr-aj website<\/span><\/a><\/u>, the website is under the supervision of Ayatollah Mohammad Hussaini Qazwini.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h1 class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\"><a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/vali-asr.png\" rel=\"external nofollow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-3578 alignright\" src=\"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/vali-asr-150x150.png\" alt=\"vali-asr\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/vali-asr-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/vali-asr-250x250.png 250w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/vali-asr-62x62.png 62w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/vali-asr-184x184.png 184w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/><\/a><\/span><\/h1>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0As we can see, the refutation includes a statement from Imam Ahmad in which he strongly denounces Mu\u2019ath bin Al-Muthanna, a narrator of the hadith. However, upon returning to the original source that is quoted, we found a completely different statement. <\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tm6\">\u201cHe (Mu\u2019ath) said: It was said to Ahmad: What of a man that purposefully does not pray the <\/span><em><span class=\"tm7\">witr<\/span><\/em><span class=\"tm6\"> prayer? He (Ahmad) said: Who does that is a bad man, he left the <\/span><em><span class=\"tm7\">sunnah<\/span><\/em><span class=\"tm6\"> of the Prophet &#8211; peace be upon him &#8211; . He then said: He is a person whose <\/span><em><span class=\"tm7\">adala<\/span><\/em><span class=\"tm6\"> has been dropped if he purposefully did not pray the <\/span><em><span class=\"tm7\">witr<\/span><\/em><span class=\"tm6\">. <\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Image-2.jpg\" rel=\"external nofollow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-3576 alignleft\" src=\"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Image-2-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"image-2\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Image-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Image-2-250x250.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Image-2-62x62.jpg 62w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Image-2-184x184.jpg 184w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/><\/a><a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Image.jpg\" rel=\"external nofollow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-3577 alignleft\" src=\"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Image-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Image-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Image-250x250.jpg 250w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Image-62x62.jpg 62w, https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Image-184x184.jpg 184w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">As we can see, the statement from Imam Ahmad has nothing to do with Mu\u2019ath. Rather, Mu\u2019ath is simply quoting from Imam Ahmad.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Conclusion<\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">In conclusion, it is clear to the objective observer that Jafar Al-Sadiq has twice as much of Abu Bakr\u2019s blood running through his veins than the blood of Ali bin Abi Talib.<br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Now, we are fully aware that being a descendant of someone does not mean that one is upon his views, however, we simply wanted to bring this information to the attention of our Shia readers, since most of them have been oblivious of this fact that was hidden away by their scholars. This reality is especially embarrassing for those that claim that Abu Bakr is from a impure lineage that actively and openly participated in lewd acts.<br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tm6\" style=\"color: #000000;\">In one of our future projects &#8211; Allah willing &#8211; , we will be compiling authentic narrations from Jafar Al-Sadiq in which he praises Abu Bakr, so stay tuned. <\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mh-excerpt\"><p>Jafar Al-Sadiq is a Descendant of Abu Bakr \u00a0 \u00a0 In the name of Allah the Most Gracious and Most Merciful&#8230; \u00a0 The following article will provide conclusive proof that Jafar Al-Sadiq is a descendant of Abu Bakr, from Sunni <a class=\"mh-excerpt-more\" href=\"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/2016\/12\/24\/jafar-al-sadiq-descendant-abu-bakr\/\" title=\"Jafar Al-Sadiq is a Descendant of Abu Bakr\">[read more]<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":3574,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[11],"tags":[17],"class_list":{"0":"post-3573","1":"post","2":"type-post","3":"status-publish","4":"format-standard","5":"has-post-thumbnail","7":"category-articles","8":"tag-abu-bakr"},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3573","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3573"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3573\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3581,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3573\/revisions\/3581"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3574"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3573"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3573"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3573"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}